msgid "Juli's dismembered body."
msgstr "由里斷肢的身體。"

msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgid "What...?"
msgstr "什麼...？"

msgid "This can't be..."
msgstr "這怎麼可能..."

msgid "Kaya's lifeless body."
msgstr "香耶毫無生氣的身體。"

msgid "Oh my god."
msgstr "我的天哪。"

msgid "She didn't deserve this..."
msgstr "她不應該受這種對待..."

msgid "Saki's headless body."
msgstr "沙紀身首異處的身體。"

msgid "No way... this can't be real..."
msgstr "不可能...不是真的..."

msgid "A school desk."
msgstr "學校的課桌。"

msgid "It feels unnatural to the touch, like it's made of stone."
msgstr "摸起來好不真實，像是用石頭做的一樣。"

msgid "Wait...!"
msgstr "等等...！"
